A refactored version to fix scope and typing in order to work with shedskin.

To install shedskin:

wget https://shedskin.googlecode.com/files/shedskin-0.9.3.tgz
tar -xzvf shedskin-0.9.3.tgz
cd shedskin-0.9.3
sudo python setup.py install
sudo apt-get install -y libgc-dev libgc1c2 libpcre++-dev libpcre++0

Then to compile py to cpp:

shedskin anneal.py

Finally, compile the C++ to a native binary:

make
